### `.gitignore`

```plaintext
# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Virtual environments
venv/
env/

# Environment variables
.env

# Jupyter Notebook checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Logs and debug files
*.log
*.out
*.err

# Data files
datasets/*.parquet
datasets/*.csv

# Docker-related
*.dockerignore
*.env

# Editor files
.vscode/
.idea/

# System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Build artifacts
dist/
build/
*.egg-info/